<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbb70b5cc-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s1778"><num value="1778">§ 1778.</num><heading> Nonprofit programs</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The food and milk service programs in schools and nonprofit institutions receiving assistance under this chapter shall be conducted on a nonprofit basis.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbb70b5cd-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/89/642/s9">Pub. L. 89–642, § 9</ref>, <date date="1966-10-11">Oct. 11, 1966</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/80/888">80 Stat. 888</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
